<b><p class = "edu">What is the coolest excuse for being late to class?</b></p>
<p>In my second year of engineering, there was a very strict professor. He was very punctual and used to insult latecomers very badly. He had strictly instructed us to either come on time or to not come at all.

One day we had to submit our assignment to him but my friend was late. Since that was the last day to submit the assignment, she couldn't skip the class. She gathered all her courage and asked the professor if she could come in.

<p>Friend: May I come in sir?</p>

He looked at her as if she had committed a sin or eaten his whole pizza.

<p>Professor: Since you know latecomers are not allowed in my lecture and yet you have dared to ask me, I hope you have a good reason or else you are in big trouble.</p>

<p>Friend: A guy hit my Activa and I had fight with him.</p>

<p>Professor: So, what do I do? That must be your fault. If you girls give right indicator and then turn left, what can a guy do?</p>

<p>Friend: Sir, this is exactly what happened.

Professor seemed extremly happy and puzzled at the same time coz his prediction was right but why did she accept it at once?</p>

<p>Professor: See. I knew it.</p>

<p>Friend: Umm…sir you have misunderstood a bit. I mean I gave right indicator and turned right only. But the guy still hit me. When I asked him about it, he had a similar reason like yours. He also thought that I would turn left after giving right indicator so he didn't slow down. So, I had a fight with him.</p>

<p>The whole class burst into laughter. Professor also had smile on his face. He couldn't believe what just happened and she got permission to get into the class.

That was one of the coolest excuses I ever witnessed to get into the class.</p>
